data.description: Ask about the $10K BUYER INCENTIVE for this one year old home, plus warranties transfer! Check out this beautiful 2-story townhome in the North Valley from the EOS series by the award winning builder, Twilight Homes. Built in 2022, this townhome features a clean design with an open floor plan, the primary bedroom suite on the main floor and two bedrooms on the second floor. Create an entertaining space in the loft area or make it a 4th bedroom, your options are endless. The back courtyard is low maintenance, enclosed and ready for your personal touches. Oversized one-car garage offers lots of additional space. All appliances currently in the home convey with the sale of the property. The lender has pre-approved this short sale, so a regular close is possible.
